#: ../../index.rst:6
msgid ""
"Welcome to **QiliSDK**, a unified Python framework for developing, "
"simulating, and running both digital and analog quantum algorithms across"
" a variety of backends (QPU, CPU, GPU) and Qilimanjaro's SpeQtrum. Its "
"modular design makes it easy to prototype circuits, build Hamiltonians, "
"design variational workflows, and deploy them on local or remote quantum "
"simulators and hardware."
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:15
msgid ""
